(4,2,'2026-02-09','2026-02-13','{"monday":{"task":"Assisted in producing the county weekly e-newsletter","comment":"Newsletter contributions are engaging"},"tuesday":{"task":"Conducted an interview with the County Executive for health on the maternal health initiative","comment":"Interview was professional and insightful"},"wednesday":{"task":"Wrote a feature article on the interview for the county website","comment":"Feature article is well-written and accurate"},"thursday":{"task":"Photographed county infrastructure projects for the development report","comment":"Photographs are professional quality"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and self-assessment","comment":"Self-assessment shows good critical reflection"}}','Approved','2026-02-09','Joseph is producing publishable quality writing for the county communications team. Very impressive.','His interview article was featured on the county Governor''s official communications report.','2026-02-13 17:00:00'),
(4,3,'2026-02-16','2026-02-20','{"monday":{"task":"Managed the county Twitter and Facebook accounts for the week","comment":"Social media engagement increased 15% this week"},"tuesday":{"task":"Produced a short video documentary on the Nairobi Urban Renewal Project","comment":"Documentary is well-produced and informative"},"wednesday":{"task":"Edited and posted the video documentary on the county YouTube channel","comment":"Video received 12,000 views in 24 hours"},"thursday":{"task":"Wrote a reflection paper on public sector media management best practices","comment":"Reflection is academically strong"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and documented social media analytics report","comment":"Analytics report shows good data literacy"}}','Approved','2026-02-16','Joseph''s documentary production skills are impressive. His social media metrics show real impact.','The documentary garnered 12,000 YouTube views. The County Communications Director is very pleased.','2026-02-20 17:00:00'),
(4,4,'2026-02-23','2026-02-27','{"monday":{"task":"Planned and executed a media day for the County Governor","comment":"Media day plan was well-executed"},"tuesday":{"task":"Prepared talking points and press briefing materials for the Governor","comment":"Briefing materials are professional and concise"},"wednesday":{"task":"Coordinated with 8 media houses for the Governor''s press briefing","comment":"Media coordination was smooth"},"thursday":{"task":"Covered the press briefing and managed Q&A session","comment":"Q&A moderation was professional"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and monthly progress report","comment":"Monthly report is comprehensive and reflective"}}','Approved','2026-02-23','Joseph coordinated a Governor''s press briefing. This is exceptional for an attachment student.','Governor Sakaja personally commended Joseph for the press briefing quality. Remarkable achievement.','2026-02-27 17:00:00'),
(4,5,'2026-03-02','2026-03-06','{"monday":{"task":"Developed a communications crisis management protocol for the county","comment":"Crisis protocol is practical and comprehensive"},"tuesday":{"task":"Presented the crisis protocol to the Communications Director","comment":"Protocol approved for implementation"},"wednesday":{"task":"Trained county communications staff on the new crisis protocol","comment":"Training was well-received"},"thursday":{"task":"Conducted media monitoring and produced a daily press review","comment":"Press review is comprehensive and insightful"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and crisis protocol documentation","comment":"Protocol documentation is professional"}}','Approved','2026-03-02','Joseph''s crisis communications protocol has been formally adopted by Nairobi County. Extraordinary.','The protocol Joseph developed is now county policy. An incredible student contribution to public governance.','2026-03-06 17:00:00'),
(4,6,'2026-03-09','2026-03-13','{"monday":{"task":"Produced a 3-part investigative series on Nairobi housing crisis for the county blog","comment":"Investigative series is thoroughly researched"},"tuesday":{"task":"Conducted interviews with 6 housing stakeholders for the investigative series","comment":"Interview techniques are professional"},"wednesday":{"task":"Published part 1 of the investigative housing series","comment":"Part 1 received 8,000 website visits"},"thursday":{"task":"Published part 2 - housing stakeholder perspectives","comment":"Part 2 generated significant public debate"},"friday":{"task":"Published part 3 - policy recommendations. Submitted logbook.","comment":"Series earned county communications team a government award"}}','Approved','2026-03-09','Joseph''s investigative series contributed to the county communication team receiving a national award.','The investigative series contributed to an emergency housing policy review at county level.','2026-03-13 17:00:00'),
(4,7,'2026-03-16','2026-03-20','{"monday":{"task":"Represented Nairobi County at the Kenya Government Communications conference","comment":"Excellent county representation"},"tuesday":{"task":"Presented the county''s digital communications strategy at the conference","comment":"Presentation was received with high praise"},"wednesday":{"task":"Networked with government communications professionals across Kenya","comment":"Built valuable professional relationships"},"thursday":{"task":"Wrote a comprehensive conference report for the Communications Director","comment":"Report captures key conference takeaways"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and conference reflection","comment":"Reflection shows excellent professional growth"}}','Approved','2026-03-16','Joseph represented Nairobi County at a national government conference. Extraordinary for a student.','His conference presentation on digital communications is being shared across county governments.','2026-03-20 17:00:00'),
(4,8,'2026-03-23','2026-03-27','{"monday":{"task":"Completed comprehensive handover documentation for all communications projects","comment":"Handover is thorough and well-organized"},"tuesday":{"task":"Trained the incoming communications intern on county media protocols","comment":"Peer training was effective and professional"},"wednesday":{"task":"Compiled a portfolio of all communications work produced during attachment","comment":"Portfolio is impressive and professionally curated"},"thursday":{"task":"Prepared final attachment report incorporating all supervisor comments","comment":"Final report is of professional quality"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and final report to academic supervisor","comment":"Final report endorsed with commendation"}}','Approved','2026-03-23','Joseph''s attachment portfolio is being added to the faculty achievement showcase. Exceptional work.','His portfolio will be featured in the county annual communications report as an example of excellence.','2026-03-27 17:00:00'),
(4,9,'2026-03-30','2026-04-03','{"monday":{"task":"Collected all clearance signatures from county department heads","comment":"Clearance obtained ahead of schedule"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended county farewell event and shared attachment lessons with county team","comment":"Farewell remarks were moving and professional"},"wednesday":{"task":"Completed county exit evaluation and performance appraisal","comment":"Appraisal: Outstanding in all 6 categories"},"thursday":{"task":"Filed all logbook and documentation in the county HR system","comment":"System upload confirmed by HR coordinator"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and confirmed attachment completion","comment":"Attachment completion confirmed"}}','Approved','2026-03-30','Joseph has completed the most commended attachment placement in the faculty this semester.','Outstanding appraisal across all 6 categories. Joseph is invited to rejoin as a paid communications officer.','2026-04-03 17:00:00'),
(4,10,'2026-04-06','2026-04-08','{"monday":{"task":"Completed university online attachment evaluation system","comment":"Detailed evaluation submitted"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended post-attachment faculty debrief for the communications students cohort","comment":"Shared insights benefited the entire cohort"},"wednesday":{"task":"Submitted all remaining university attachment documentation","comment":"All requirements fulfilled"},"thursday":{"task":"N/A - Good Friday Public Holiday","comment":""},"friday":{"task":"N/A - Easter Monday Public Holiday","comment":""}}','Approved','2026-04-06','Joseph has met all university attachment requirements. His final report is a model for future students.','County HR has provided the highest possible reference letter for Joseph. A true communications star.','2026-04-08 17:00:00'),
(4,11,'2026-04-13','2026-04-17','{"monday":{"task":"Filed all physical attachment documentation with the department office","comment":"Physical requirements all fulfilled"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended faculty attachment completion recognition ceremony","comment":"Recognized as top performer in the cohort"},"wednesday":{"task":"Completed remaining online portal submissions","comment":"All portal submissions confirmed"},"thursday":{"task":"Post-attachment career counselling session with faculty advisor","comment":"Advisor recommends Joseph for media excellence scholarship"},"friday":{"task":"Attachment requirements fully completed","comment":"Confirmed by faculty attachments officer"}}','Approved','2026-04-13','Joseph is the top-performing attachment student in the Journalism cohort this semester.','Nairobi County Communications believes Joseph will be one of Kenya''s leading journalists. Proud.','2026-04-17 17:00:00'),
(4,12,'2026-04-22','2026-04-25','{"monday":{"task":"Post-attachment debrief with academic supervisor","comment":"Insightful and mature debrief discussion"},"tuesday":{"task":"Submitted final physical copies of all attachment documents","comment":"All documents received and receipted"},"wednesday":{"task":"Attachment completion ceremony participation","comment":"Received faculty dean commendation"},"thursday":{"task":"Attachment officially complete - all requirements fulfilled","comment":"Confirmed by university attachments office"},"friday":{"task":"N/A - Attachment period concluded","comment":""}}','Approved','2026-04-22','Joseph Mutua has completed his attachment with the highest commendation. A model for all students.','Nairobi County congratulates Joseph on a remarkable attachment. We look forward to working with him again.','2026-04-25 17:00:00');

