(5,1,'2026-02-02','2026-02-06','{"monday":{"task":"Orientation to KRA ICT Department and systems architecture overview","comment":"Strong foundational ICT knowledge evident"},"tuesday":{"task":"Reviewed KRA iTax system architecture and API documentation","comment":"Quick grasp of complex government systems"},"wednesday":{"task":"Set up development environment and reviewed existing codebase","comment":"Setup completed without assistance"},"thursday":{"task":"Attended sprint planning and was assigned to the taxpayer services portal team","comment":"Good agile methodology understanding"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted first logbook","comment":"Reflective and detailed first entry"}}','Approved','2026-02-02','Brenda shows exceptional software engineering potential. Excellent start at KRA.','Brenda was productive from day one. The development team is impressed with her technical depth.','2026-02-06 17:00:00'),
(5,2,'2026-02-09','2026-02-13','{"monday":{"task":"Developed a REST API for taxpayer filing status lookup","comment":"API is clean, documented and functional"},"tuesday":{"task":"Wrote comprehensive unit tests achieving 90% code coverage","comment":"Test coverage is exceptional"},"wednesday":{"task":"Participated in sprint retrospective and contributed improvement suggestions","comment":"Suggestions were adopted by the team"},"thursday":{"task":"Integrated the filing status API with the iTax front-end portal","comment":"Integration tested and deployed to staging"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and documented API","comment":"Documentation is developer-friendly"}}','Approved','2026-02-09','Brenda''s API is being considered for production deployment. Extraordinary week.','Her 90% test coverage is better than most senior developers achieve. Remarkable student.','2026-02-13 17:00:00'),
(5,3,'2026-02-16','2026-02-20','{"monday":{"task":"Built a data validation module for VAT return submissions","comment":"Validation rules are comprehensive and accurate"},"tuesday":{"task":"Implemented error handling and user-friendly error messages","comment":"Error handling significantly improves UX"},"wednesday":{"task":"Conducted code review for three junior developer pull requests","comment":"Reviews were constructive and technically accurate"},"thursday":{"task":"Presented code improvements in the weekly engineering meeting","comment":"Presentation was technically impressive"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook with technical reflection","comment":"Technical depth of reflection is excellent"}}','Approved','2026-02-16','Brenda is conducting code reviews for more experienced developers. Extraordinary capability.','She presented to the CTO this week and received a commendation. Exceptional student.','2026-02-20 17:00:00'),
(5,4,'2026-02-23','2026-02-27','{"monday":{"task":"Developed automated report generation module for the KRA compliance dashboard","comment":"Report module is efficient and accurate"},"tuesday":{"task":"Optimized slow SQL queries reducing execution time by 60%","comment":"Significant performance improvement"},"wednesday":{"task":"Attended a Kenya CyberSecurity Forum as KRA representative","comment":"Excellent representation of KRA"},"thursday":{"task":"Presented cybersecurity insights to the KRA development team","comment":"Insights directly applicable to the project"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and monthly progress report","comment":"Monthly report is comprehensive"}}','Approved','2026-02-23','Brenda represented KRA at a national cybersecurity forum. Phenomenal achievement for a student.','Her SQL optimizations saved the government KES 200,000 in cloud computing costs monthly.','2026-02-27 17:00:00'),
(5,5,'2026-03-02','2026-03-06','{"monday":{"task":"Led the development of a taxpayer mobile app prototype using React Native","comment":"Mobile app prototype is polished and functional"},"tuesday":{"task":"Conducted user testing with 10 KRA staff members on the mobile prototype","comment":"User testing results are positive"},"wednesday":{"task":"Iterated on prototype based on user testing feedback","comment":"Iterations improved UX significantly"},"thursday":{"task":"Presented the mobile prototype to the KRA Commissioner for Internal Revenue","comment":"Commissioner approved prototype for further development"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook with prototype development reflection","comment":"Reflection shows excellent product thinking"}}','Approved','2026-03-02','Brenda''s mobile prototype received Commissioner approval. Unprecedented for an attachment student.','Commissioner approved the prototype, citing it as the best taxpayer engagement innovation this year.','2026-03-06 17:00:00'),
