(5,7,'2026-03-16','2026-03-20','{"monday":{"task":"Deployed the anomaly detection ML system to KRA production environment","comment":"Production deployment completed successfully"},"tuesday":{"task":"Monitored ML system performance in production for 48 hours","comment":"System performing at 89% precision in production"},"wednesday":{"task":"Prepared a technical case study on the ML fraud detection implementation","comment":"Case study is of conference paper quality"},"thursday":{"task":"Submitted case study to the Africa Tax Technology Conference for presentation","comment":"Conference accepted the submission"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and collected supervisor endorsement","comment":"Endorsement obtained with highest commendation"}}','Approved','2026-03-16','Brenda''s case study was accepted by the Africa Tax Technology Conference. Unprecedented achievement.','A student''s work presented at a continental conference. KRA is enormously proud of Brenda.','2026-03-20 17:00:00'),
(5,8,'2026-03-23','2026-03-27','{"monday":{"task":"Completed comprehensive technical handover documentation","comment":"Handover documentation is thorough and clear"},"tuesday":{"task":"Trained KRA development team on the ML system maintenance and monitoring","comment":"Training was effective and well-received"},"wednesday":{"task":"Conducted code refactoring session to improve maintainability of all systems built","comment":"Code quality significantly improved"},"thursday":{"task":"Completed final attachment report and submitted to academic supervisor","comment":"Report is of research paper quality"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and final report endorsed by academic supervisor","comment":"Endorsed with highest academic commendation"}}','Approved','2026-03-23','Brenda''s final report is being considered for the best attachment report award at the faculty.','KRA will be presenting Brenda''s final report to the Treasury as evidence of innovation in public service.','2026-03-27 17:00:00'),
(5,9,'2026-03-30','2026-04-03','{"monday":{"task":"Collected all KRA department clearance signatures","comment":"All clearances obtained"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended KRA farewell function and received the KRA Innovator of the Year Award","comment":"First intern to receive this award in KRA history"},"wednesday":{"task":"Completed KRA exit interview and performance evaluation","comment":"Performance rating: Outstanding"},"thursday":{"task":"Filed all documentation in the KRA HR system","comment":"System upload confirmed"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook and confirmed attachment conclusion","comment":"Attachment completed by KRA"}}','Approved','2026-03-30','Brenda won the KRA Innovator of the Year Award - first intern in KRA history to receive this.','A standing ovation from the entire KRA ICT department. The youngest innovator in KRA history.','2026-04-03 17:00:00'),
(5,10,'2026-04-06','2026-04-08','{"monday":{"task":"Completed university attachment evaluation and all exit surveys","comment":"Evaluation submitted with detailed feedback"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended university post-attachment cohort debrief","comment":"Inspired the entire cohort with her KRA experience"},"wednesday":{"task":"Filed all university attachment portal submissions","comment":"All submissions confirmed"},"thursday":{"task":"N/A - Good Friday Public Holiday","comment":""},"friday":{"task":"N/A - Easter Monday Public Holiday","comment":""}}','Approved','2026-04-06','Brenda has completed the most impactful software engineering attachment in the faculty''s history.','Full-time software engineer position offered by KRA. Brenda is a once-in-a-decade talent.','2026-04-08 17:00:00'),
(5,11,'2026-04-13','2026-04-17','{"monday":{"task":"Submitted all physical attachment documents to the department office","comment":"All requirements fulfilled"},"tuesday":{"task":"Attended faculty attachment awards ceremony","comment":"Received the Top Attachment Student award"},"wednesday":{"task":"Post-attachment career counselling session","comment":"Counsellor recommends Brenda for national engineering scholarship"},"thursday":{"task":"Completed all remaining documentation requirements","comment":"All requirements confirmed completed"},"friday":{"task":"Attachment officially concluded by faculty coordinator","comment":"Highest distinction confirmed"}}','Approved','2026-04-13','Brenda Chepkemoi wins the faculty Top Attachment Student award. An extraordinary achievement.','KRA thanks the university for producing brilliant talents like Brenda. A national asset.','2026-04-17 17:00:00'),
(5,12,'2026-04-22','2026-04-25','{"monday":{"task":"Post-attachment academic debrief and final documentation verification","comment":"All documentation verified and complete"},"tuesday":{"task":"Submitted final physical copies of all attachment documents","comment":"Received and receipted"},"wednesday":{"task":"Attended and participated in attachment completion ceremony","comment":"Received dean''s special commendation"},"thursday":{"task":"Attachment officially complete - all requirements fulfilled","comment":"Confirmed by attachments office"},"friday":{"task":"N/A - Attachment period concluded","comment":""}}','Approved','2026-04-22','Brenda Chepkemoi - the most outstanding software engineering attachment student in faculty history.','KRA is proud of Brenda''s contributions. Her work protects Kenyan taxpayers. A national hero.','2026-04-25 17:00:00');

