(15,7,'2026-03-16','2026-03-20','{"monday":{"task":"Conducted a financial sustainability analysis of KNH''s revenue and cost structure","comment":"Financial sustainability analysis is comprehensive"},"tuesday":{"task":"Prepared policy recommendations for improving KNH financial sustainability","comment":"Recommendations are evidence-based and practical"},"wednesday":{"task":"Presented sustainability analysis to the KNH Board Finance Subcommittee","comment":"Board was highly impressed with the analysis"},"thursday":{"task":"Board approved 2 of Emily''s 5 financial sustainability recommendations","comment":"Direct policy impact from a student"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted logbook endorsed by KNH CFO","comment":"CFO''s endorsement is the highest praise"}}','Approved','2026-03-16','Emily presented to the KNH Board and had 2 recommendations adopted. Extraordinary policy impact.','Board-level adoption of student recommendations. Emily is a future healthcare finance administrator.','2026-03-20 17:00:00'),
(15,8,'2026-03-23','2026-03-27','{"monday":{"task":"Completed comprehensive finance handover documentation","comment":"Handover is thorough and well-organized"},"tuesday":{"task":"Submitted final attachment report to academic supervisor","comment":"Report endorsed with highest commendation"},"wednesday":{"task":"Exit interview and performance evaluation at KNH","comment":"Rating: Outstanding"},"thursday":{"task":"Collected all KNH clearance signatures from 4 departments","comment":"Clearance process in progress"},"friday":{"task":"Submitted final logbook","comment":"Professional and comprehensive"}}','Approved','2026-03-23','Emily''s final report is outstanding. The Business and Economics faculty is tremendously proud.','KNH rates Emily Outstanding. Her board-level impact and revenue model are remarkable contributions.','2026-03-27 17:00:00'),
