(7, 18, 16, '2026-01-22', 'Pending', 'uploads/resumes/resume_student_16.pdf', 'My public administration studies combined with genuine interest in digital governance make the Ministry of ICT internship a perfect fit. I want to contribute to Kenya''s digital economy policy.'),
