(9, 20, 10, '2026-01-23', 'Pending', 'uploads/resumes/resume_student_10.pdf', 'PwC''s Deals and Assurance practices align perfectly with my investment banking and financial analysis background. An audit perspective from PwC would round out my finance skill set comprehensively.'),
(9, 20, 15, '2026-01-25', 'Pending', 'uploads/resumes/resume_student_15.pdf', 'Having worked in healthcare finance at KNH, I am interested in how external audit examines complex sector organizations. PwC''s healthcare and public sector audit practice would be an excellent learning environment.'),
